<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Text column -->
      <div>
        <p class="reveal text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold mb-4 font-medium">Our Story</p>
        <h2 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 font-playfair text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-8 leading-tight">
          A little slice<br />of <em>home</em>
        </h2>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 divider-gold mb-8"></div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 space-y-5 text-bronze-light leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Born from the heart of Valley Orchid Farms in Canton, Texas, Gugu Gifts carries forward a tradition of warmth, care, and the joy of giving. We've always believed that the best gifts feel personal &mdash; like they were chosen by a friend who truly knows you.
          </p>
          <p>
            Now, we're bringing that same spirit to Terrell. Our curated collection blends beloved brands like Voluspa and Julie Vos with locally crafted honey, artisan soaps, and one-of-a-kind finds that you won't see everywhere else.
          </p>
          <p>
            Every item on our shelves is selected with intention &mdash; to bring beauty, meaning, and a little bit of luxury to your everyday life. Whether you're treating yourself or finding the perfect gift, we want you to feel at home the moment you walk through our door.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Decorative column -->
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 relative hidden md:block">
        <div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cream-dark via-gold/10 to-sage/10 border border-gold/20 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Decorative botanical illustration -->
          <svg viewBox="0 0 200 260" class="w-48 h-auto text-gold/25" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.75">
            <!-- Stem -->
            <path d="M100 240 C100 200 95 160 100 120 C105 80 100 50 100 20" />
